  "steps": [
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ひだまりストア・閉店後の売り場――",
      "bg": "images/assets/bg/bg_hidamari_store_salesfloor_night.png",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、今日の棚卸し助かった。\nおかげで閉店作業、かなり早く終わったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今日は、言わなくていいって言わないんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "言ったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも、前より小さめに言った。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そこは調整してるのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "練習だから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "なるほど。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "なるほどって言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "謝らなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空はレジ横の小さなラックを整える。\nそこには地域イベントのチラシが何枚か置かれていた。\n夜空の指が、そのうち一枚で止まる。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それ、何のチラシだ？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……別に。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "別に、で隠す時は少し気になる。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "気にしなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そうか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……そこで引くのもずるい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "じゃあ、気にする。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "それもずるい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "難しいな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "難しくしてるのは、ぼく。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "最近、だいぶ自分で言うようになったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "褒めないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今のは褒めたつもりじゃなかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも、少し褒めてた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ばれたか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ばれる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空はチラシを手に取り、店長の方へ差し出す。\nそこには、羽白湖の星空観察会の案内が載っていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "羽白湖、星空観察会……。\nへえ、週末の夜にやるんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、こういうの気になるのか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……美空が好きそうだから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "美空が？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "空が広く見える場所、好きって言ってたでしょ。\n潮見浜でも言ってた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "覚えてるんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "覚えてる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空は？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぼく？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空は、気にならないのか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "プラネタリウムの時も、星を見てた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "プラネタリウムなんだから見るでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それ、前にも聞いたな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "便利だから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "でも、今回は本物の星だ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "見てみたい？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……美空が行くなら。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空は？"
