        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空の話だからな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……そういうの、まだ慣れない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "慣れなくていい。\nでも、聞く。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ずるい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "認めないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――そこへ、美空が売り場奥から戻ってくる。\n手には閉店チェック用のファイルを持っていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "あ、羽白湖のチラシですね。",
